Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神代玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔界的大门势必会打开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有碍事的人统统受死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.50,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你的父亲那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.12,0:00:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了爸爸？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能过去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是杀死爸爸的仇人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.91,0:00:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐就请逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们就由千寻我来挡住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我去死吧！白魔法师！！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}借千之风 寻找美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟～ 要穿进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.54,0:02:57.72,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(936,974)}Ignis
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.92,0:03:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逗你玩的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我放下 我也要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我放下 把我放下来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:33.35,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}杀魔女 毁魔窟…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛禽兽！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.86,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(928,974)}Avis Rapax
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然把魔物连续召唤过来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错的仿造品对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人不也很欢乐的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连小命被盯上了也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许愚弄大小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅没降临呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么反应都没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅或许就在附近也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通灵板与通灵术都不行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只剩这个了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测棒怎么可能把灵召唤出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有反应了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惨烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼火 是鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅一定就在那里面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀魔女 毁魔窟…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是鬼火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙是要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降灵成功了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘还好好活着呢 赶紧逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:48.25,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}杀魔女 杀魔女 杀魔女…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.37,0:05:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赖嘛 白魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就看看 你的气势能撑多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心 那位大人很强大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到城外去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑魔女的目标是你 请稍事忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了我们的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你去到大小姐那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 好可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是用这种淫荡的声音去魅惑那个人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美风小姐 我一直被你骗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 要对他下手简直不费吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这镇上的人们也是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀魔女 毁魔窟…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦卖噶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.39,0:07:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又咋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 梢消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道那女孩总有一天会妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在校外把她干掉倒是不易
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.21,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是那个男人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托他以后马上就放我进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 后面！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是神马东西啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 这边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对他用了什么卑鄙手段？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是给他温柔地挠了挠痒痒罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加报酬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一年份的布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 拜托你们两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人真是单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给点甜头就摇头摆尾了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个人的心灵是纯净无瑕的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想的东西多着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是纯洁的爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满盈的全是欲望啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人都是只想满足自己欲望的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会用爱填满一切！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是你的幻觉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱可以构建起幸福的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Smile！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也忙着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱什么的说到底还不是为了肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱是发自内心的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就当一辈子爱的魔法师吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 我和那个人接吻过了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…副校长她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人逃走什么的 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅大人你保护好自己的生命 是纯一郎大人的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爸爸他已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙杀了爸爸 甚至连副校长也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还想毁灭世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能只是默默地看着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让那样的事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 坐上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.06,0:10:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有打倒黑魔女的办法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.37,0:10:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 一个都没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我砍了你 神代玛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副校长…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能帮我转达给大小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯一郎大人还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.53,0:12:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们用和之前一样的魔法欺骗了敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 校长…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安倍老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的祈愿 化作翱翔的白鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽翼啊 请为他指引
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往那远离悲伤 没有痛苦 欢乐萦绕的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往那守候着幸福的明日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往那光芒永驻的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑木！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的正好 带我去玛雅那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好没 亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上来！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀魔女 捣魔窟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.25,0:14:15.94,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}杀魔女 捣魔窟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.09,0:14:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀魔女～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是梢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢也真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腐黑咒！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.55,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(928,974)}Nigredo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.55,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nigredo：炼金术用语中指代腐败或分解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 爸爸的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为已经烧掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是别的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副校长事先把里面的内容交换了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这上面写着封印你的咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我们只是在一味乱窜而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒黑魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要作为笔记继承人的你和学院的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了发动咒语 我们要去瓦尔德施泰因学院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逼上绝路的 其实是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笔记…！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法发动的话就仅仅是堆纸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个学校就是你的墓碑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过嘛 世界毁灭的话 这里也会消失就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会…让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 都要死的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 都说了让你等等的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.07,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}玛雅 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要那么着急嘛 马上就能两人独处了嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.35,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}现在就来救你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就会享有永远的快乐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.52,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}玛雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师～我想无视别人是不好的哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心跳不已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我的身体 是这样的愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文明！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙就是诺查丹玛斯之钥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞毛啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:03.33,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(964,974)}Debris magia territory
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破碎魔法领域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 那个确实是消灭魔鬼的咒语啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遗憾 由你来诵读的话就没效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.73,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(964,974)}Debris magia territory
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破碎魔法领域
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.37,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(968,974)}Leno nenia finis
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安详叹歌终焉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:27.29,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(968,974)}Leno nenia finis
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安详叹歌终焉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.73,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(976,974)}Regina canorus
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王呵 轻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.46,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(976,974)}Regina canorus
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王呵 轻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:35.40,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(968,974)}Domina cantlena
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一曲摇篮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.71,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(968,974)}Domina cantlena
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一曲摇篮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.19,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(936,974)}Mise…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.98,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(964,974)}Miserere area
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相怜之地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.97,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(964,974)}Miserere area
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相怜之地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能！为什么还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:57.90,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(932,974)}Lucis ortho
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万丈流明！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 我的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:01.32,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Lucis ortho
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}万丈流明！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(940,974)}Leo…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.99,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来 停下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:13.35,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(940,974)}Leo ortus en necto
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮心我缚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点疼…和玛雅打的比起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你这变态～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:33.54,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(940,974)}Leo ortus en necto
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狮心我缚！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.10,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(932,974)}Mille gladius
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千刃向汝！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀魔女…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为 为什么连你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…消灭一切魔物…的咒语…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于黑暗中诞生之物…便要回归于黑暗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿您…好运…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你知道咒语是哪一页
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是副校长…千寻小姐她告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.83,0:21:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是No. 6
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙已经找到 并且已经毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去外面吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是我们的胜利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 文明
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的未来会在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我们会见到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.84,0:23:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要回未来去…了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末超自然学院
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.32,0:24:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大结局 玛雅的文明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因超自然 我们相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
